[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][I]Tired of harvesting your crops while wearing steel plate armor? [/I][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR] [/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][I]Sick of mining ore in a 100 pound set of orcish armor? [/I][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR] [/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][I]This mod adds a new set of clothing custom taliored for hard working folks. [/I][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR] [/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][I]Craftable at any tanning rack, no armor protection, purely clothing. Wear around town, at the mines, the lumber mill, or anywhere else. [/I][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR] [/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][B][I]This mod features BBP (or whatever it's called....the boobs bounce, that's all I know) so [URL=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800]XP32 Maximum Skeleton[/URL] is required. Base body is built from [URL=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36992/?]SevenBase body replacer[/URL], which is also required. CTD will occur if you do not install XP32 Maximum Skeleton. [/I][/B][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][B][I][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype][/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/I][/B] [/CENTER]
[CENTER][B][I][COLOR=#92d050][SIZE=5][FONT=Palatino Linotype]Please post any feedback in comments section. And feel free to check out my other mods.[/FONT][/SIZE][/COLOR][/I][/B][/CENTER]
